Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀨田 瀨田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.94,0:01:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄 志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.74,0:01:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左臉頰有十字刀疤的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和腰上掛著日本刀的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.58,0:01:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正向我們這間房子走來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.78,0:02:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還沒去拜碼頭\N他們就特別跑來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不愧是前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.92,0:02:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎 你去迎接他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.36,0:02:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.70,0:02:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有叫尖角準備打前鋒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.10,0:02:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角他隨時都在備戰狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十六話\N穿越幕末之時\N志志雄與劍心的對峙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.98,0:02:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是緋村拔刀齊和齊藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好不要把刀尖對著志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.39,0:02:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如你們不想變成那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤小心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.00,0:02:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是殺死大久保的那個男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.07,0:02:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別緊張 我今天只負責帶路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 我沒有佩刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.71,0:03:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄在後面的房間等你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警戒狀態還不會開打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下嘛！榮次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是叫你不要管我的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小聲一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去就算沒有做壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.96,0:03:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親 母親 還有哥哥們\N都被尖角那小子殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一回想起來就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少讓我親手為哥哥報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心情我懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.27,0:04:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那房子裏\N志志雄的兵隊正嚴秘警戒著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.78,0:04:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡亂闖進那房子的話\N只會被折磨死而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你見到尖角那小子之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…到底要我怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.82,0:04:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣才能替大家報仇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我來辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.26,0:04:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弄得他們大吃一驚聲東擊西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聲東擊西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算怎麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.14,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一給你信號你就快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.34,0:04:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.78,0:04:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了\N什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.88,0:04:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.69,0:04:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噓！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼？\N會不會是貓頭鷹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好大驚小怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？是不是令你另眼相看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.70,0:04:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.88,0:05:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄 泡完澡喝杯酒吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.78,0:05:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.65,0:05:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是志志雄真實嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少也加個稱謂吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.86,0:05:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒禮貌的前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.20,0:05:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意 你也沒什麼禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.57,0:05:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 呆呆地站在這兒好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.47,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是拔刀齊的話\N會一個箭步殺到志志雄身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.14,0:05:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會的 緋村和齊藤你不同\N絕對不會耍小人偷襲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼找上這個村子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.22,0:05:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要的是整個日本\N不是一 兩個小村莊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.37,0:06:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏涌出的溫泉\N治療被火燙傷的皮膚最有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.54,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是其他洗溫泉的客人\N看到我這樣子會害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.84,0:06:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才把這裏佔為己有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.61,0:06:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只為了這種事\N就要佔領這村子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑的 開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.99,0:06:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然和傳說中一樣\N你的性格超級認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要像小女生那樣直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰在背後議論我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.38,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是蒼紫就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿下這村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.75,0:07:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是要做制壓東海地區\N的軍事據點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.19,0:07:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過\N對這裏的溫泉真的很滿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.13,0:07:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.33,0:07:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後還要把這裏當做\N向明治政府報復的據點是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身繃帶的小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.20,0:07:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新撰組三番隊隊長 齊藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.24,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和拔刀齊比起來\N你我的性質比較接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.24,0:07:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來以為你會比較懂我\N事實不然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.61,0:07:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.52,0:07:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在拔刀齊之後\N接任影子殺人一職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為維新政府賣命的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.33,0:07:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那些人不斷的利用我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.23,0:07:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我知道太多秘密之後\N企圖殺我滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.55,0:08:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後還把我燒得體無完膚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 我命大沒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是因為火傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.50,0:08:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我身體變得\N常人無法想像的高熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是地獄烈火的殘火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.54,0:08:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在我體內\N不停的繼續燃燒著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.55,0:08:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在的我\N並不想對那些人報復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.09,0:08:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至還很感謝他們呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.72,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這身傷\N教了我許多刻骨銘心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太相信的話就會被出賣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疏忽大意的話就會被殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被殺害之前要先殺了對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.94,0:09:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的好男人不管變什麼樣\N女人都會自已找上門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣\N你能不能不要再惹事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了你一個人\N讓我在全日本跑來跑去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很累人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.52,0:09:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我和前輩\N同樣都是活過幕府末期的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.29,0:09:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不懂我的感覺呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說是攘夷 勤王 佐幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.64,0:09:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果幕府末期\N也只不過是戰國以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.41,0:09:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經過三百年至今的\N佐幕派一個動亂時期而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐幕派 倒幕派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.34,0:09:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過是各自高舉著\N自已所主張的正義錦旗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天爭鬥殺戮的動亂時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.68,0:09:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生在那樣的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.02,0:09:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人都會想\N試著去爭奪天下的霸權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是結果呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被暗殺之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於養好傷重出江湖一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動亂結束\N跑出個明治政府來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.41,0:10:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且連殺我一個人都辦不到\N無能的政府罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國家怎麼能交給這樣的政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.62,0:10:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動亂結束的話\N我再弄一個出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要奪得霸權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.39,0:10:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後我要讓這個國家變強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.66,0:10:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是\N我要奪得這國家的正義之論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.17,0:10:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為你的正義流血的\N並不是你自已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.64,0:10:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流血喪命的\N是那些和平過日的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這世界終究是弱肉強食的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩好像並不認同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.29,0:11:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不允許再有人\N為了你一個人的假正義流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤 你認為呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.77,0:11:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不像他喜歡高談闊論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.27,0:11:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來殺死志志雄\N比較像我的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真要動手的話我一定奉陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.71,0:11:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然要開打\N不如到花之京都也滿好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果一定要動手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.72,0:11:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的對手\N是經濟本新月村的尖角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈…尖角你還是那麼粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角…就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.04,0:11:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死榮次父母的那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.11,0:11:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.55,0:11:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.05,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼哼哼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.92,0:12:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼沒有想像中那麼精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.29,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齊 你不夠兇狠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是和榮次約定好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.31,0:12:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在志志雄的面前打倒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想打倒我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.02,0:12:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.53,0:12:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前為止殺了99個人的尖角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.40,0:12:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一百個要殺的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.64,0:12:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,99個人？哼！還真殺了不少人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中有名的神速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是比速度的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角是不會輸他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊看刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.87,0:13:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！殺人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有在背後逃跑的能力嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是膽小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這點本事的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.04,0:13:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我有你所欠缺的猛力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.62,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我手上的懷劍\N會將這兩項發揮到極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.06,0:14:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警備比想像中還要嚴密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.63,0:14:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣沒辦法接近房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角那小子到底會在哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛入這檔事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.41,0:14:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,善於聲東擊西的我最厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.91,0:14:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要穩如泰山 咚…的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全看我的 嗚哇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 搞什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蜘蛛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳 被人發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我最討厭蜘蛛和毛毛蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都什麼時候了 你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.14,0:15:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰？誰躲在那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.81,0:15:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成這樣沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好 你待在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.61,0:15:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.42,0:15:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！我卷田操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.89,0:15:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不會告訴壞人我的名字\N看我的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經報名出來了嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.33,0:15:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼東西 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟…糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.80,0:15:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丟臉死了 討厭討厭討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.24,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事…我才不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.48,0:15:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不乖乖開道的話我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.85,0:15:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別小看我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你笨頭笨腦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰笨頭笨腦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺！賞你怪鳥飛腿！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.53,0:16:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿！第一回合結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.82,0:16:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.45,0:16:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,榮次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.99,0:16:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來帶路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶我去找尖角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.56,0:16:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！你這小鬼有殺過人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.67,0:16:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有膽量的話就下手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.84,0:16:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳！為什麼要阻止我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我照辦就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫你帶路不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…閃來閃去 閃來閃去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.56,0:17:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我的速度不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.83,0:17:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像蟑螂一樣\N你想躲到什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷入苦戰之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.67,0:17:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村一直在閃躲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒有出手攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,助他一刀之力 你看怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.85,0:17:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.92,0:17:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種對手才不想賣我的大刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.49,0:17:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛還神色自若談笑風聲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始打鬥後表情就一直那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.73,0:17:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的工夫\N點滴不漏的仔細研究著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.87,0:17:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不敢輕忽大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.04,0:17:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊當然也發覺到那視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.18,0:18:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不主動攻擊\N一直就這樣好引誘對方自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.85,0:18:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.42,0:18:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…不要太過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚啊…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳…我的腳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.04,0:18:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斷…斷掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.25,0:18:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度不減慢連續移動的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.52,0:18:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉身的時候\N身體承受的負擔超過極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.29,0:18:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說\N都以同樣速度在移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.22,0:18:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可能\N比體格弱小的你先超過極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.13,0:18:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正因為速度相同\N你的體重對身體的負擔大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡…胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.47,0:18:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從來沒碰過這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.01,0:19:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才這樣的速度\N不可能讓我的身體超過極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.51,0:19:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真笨 你還沒發覺到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.62,0:19:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊在轉身的同時\N慢慢的把速度加快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.22,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自認速度和拔刀齊一樣的你\N不自覺的中計了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.63,0:19:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是自爆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.23,0:19:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說你殺過99個人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.93,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一百個人你自已劃下句點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.70,0:19:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來大家都運用戰術來打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.18,0:19:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人 那是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒殺人 我沒殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.38,0:19:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說99個人只是虛張聲勢而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.19,0:19:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過榮次一家人是你殺的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.56,0:20:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用鼻子想也知道\N你贏不了拔刀齊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.63,0:20:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊一招也沒出你就輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.34,0:20:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我直接殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謹慎一點\N不要讓人發現知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流
